We’re beyond thrilled to bring back FLYPSHIP X AQUA for a Sunday Sundowner at Aqua | The Park, Bangalore on March 2, 2025! 🌅
Get ready for an electrifying sundown experience with Afro-diasporic sounds, high energy, and pure vibes!

 @aahannaaa_ and @mysachannn are an energetic dance duo specializing in Afro and Hip-Hop. Their unique style blends rhythm, groove, and intricate footwork, creating performances full of energy and passion. With a deep love for movement and music, they bring a fresh and dynamic presence to every stage. 

  Catch Aahana & Mysa live afro dance showcase this Sunday at Aqua The park bangalore !
